data.description: Step into this amazing golf course home in sought-after Desert Lakes Community. Imagine waking up and heading downstairs in your own PRIVATE ELEVATOR avoiding all the stairs!  Walk into your beautiful living room and watch the morning sunrise as you sip your favorite beverage and enjoy tons of natural lighting. Entertain guests with the open kitchen to the  family and nook area. The kitchen includes a convection oven microwave, electric stove, dishwasher and garbage disposal, soft close cabinets, pantry with tons of storage. The large  island even has a sink to allow you and others to make some amazing meals with plenty of room. Also, don't forget to take in the natural light with the shaded windows helping with light  control throughout the kitchen, family and nook areas. Finally, end your evening by grabbing a drink at your wet bar and walk out the primary bedroom french doors and start relaxing in  your private jacuzzi while watching the sunset. The community is also located only minutes from the Colorado River where you can enjoy watersports. Also close to casinos, shopping,  hospitals and great restaurants only minutes away. NO HOA Buyer to verify flood plain and utilities.
